Package: resourcetracker
Type: Package
Title: Nowcasting Australian Real Goods Exports from AIS Shipping Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("David", "Stephan", email = "david.stephan@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
    Running-nowcast of ABS 5302.0 quarterly real goods credits using IMF
    PortWatch AIS tonnage, ABS 5368.0 monthly trade values, and FRED
    commodity prices. Bridge regressions per commodity (iron ore, coal,
    LNG, other) feed a quarterly aggregate with bootstrap uncertainty
    bands that shrink as the quarter is observed.
